@DaveHPT Let's try a different approach - we are lost in the semantics.

Should treating doctors be entitled to treat without limitation, interference, etc?

Should individuals be entitled to abstain from treatment?

@seancondev MY approach of "single treatment, one size fits all"?

lol that's funny. 

"A balanced approach" is a thing that sounds good and reasonable. But pretending that anti-vaxers aren't anti-vaxers and "a balanced approach" is all they actually want is another thing entirely.
